high_descs: Move to the kitchen table to the right of the sink
Pick up a tomato from the table
Move to the microwave to the left of the sink
Place the tomato inside the microwave and close the door, microwave it for a moment before removing the tomato and closing the door
Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Place the tomato on to the counter to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato onto the counter to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn right to the white table
Grab the tomato on the table
Turn around, and turn right, walk to the microwave
Open the microwave, put the tomato on the plate, close the microwave, turn on the microwave, open the microwave, take the tomato out, close the microwave
Turn right, walk to the right side of the sink
Put the tomato down by the knife on the counter
anns.task_desc: Cook the tomato with microwave, put it on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the small white table.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, then place the tomato inside, close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave door, remove the tomato, and close the door.
Turn to your right and walk across the room to the end of the kitchen counter.
Put the heated tomato on the counter in front and to the right of the plastic container.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato on the kitchen counter.
